    • Method Detail

      • setTiltStartTimeIntervalMs

        @NonNull
T setTiltStartTimeIntervalMs​(long tiltStartTimeInterval)
        Sets time interval between neutral tilt step and first tilt step (left, right, top or down). By default, this is set to DEFAULT_TILT_START_TIME_INTERVAL_MS.
        Parameters:
        tiltStartTimeInterval - time interval between neutral tilt step and first tilt step.
        Returns:
        this options object.

      • setTiltStepTimeoutIntervalMs

        @NonNull
T setTiltStepTimeoutIntervalMs​(long tiltStepTimeoutInterval)
        Sets timeout interval for each tilt step. To disable the timeout, set it to TIME_INFINITY. By default, this is set to DEFAULT_TILT_STEP_TIMEOUT_INTERVAL_MS.
        Parameters:
        tiltStepTimeoutInterval - timeout interval for each tilt step.
        Returns:
        this options object.

      • setShowTooltipTimeIntervalMs

        @NonNull
T setShowTooltipTimeIntervalMs​(long showTooltipTimeIntervalMs)
        Sets time interval between the start of the tilt step and displaying the help tooltip. Help tooltip is displayed only once. By default, this is set to DEFAULT_SHOW_TOOLTIP_TIME_INTERVAL_MS.
        Parameters:
        showTooltipTimeIntervalMs - time interval between the start of the tilt step and displaying the help tooltip.
        Returns:
        this options object.
